title: toolbar Macro (Examples)

This example create a replica of ~TiddlyWiki ~PageControls:

<$macrocall $name=".example" n="1" eg="""<div class="tc-page-controls">
<<toolbar "$:/tags/PageControls" "$:/config/PageControlButtons/Visibility/">>
</div>"""/>


This example create a replica of ~TiddlyWiki ~PageControls with class "//tc-btn-rounded//", without change the general style for toolbar buttons:

<$macrocall $name=".example" n="2" eg="""<div class="tc-page-controls">
<<toolbar "$:/tags/PageControls" "$:/config/PageControlButtons/Visibility/" "tc-btn-rounded">>
</div>"""/>


This example create a replica of drop-down of the ~ViewToolbar:

<$macrocall $name=".example" n="3" eg="""<div class="tc-titlebar tc-tiddler-controls" style="float:initial; width: 380px;">
<div class="tc-drop-down">
<<toolbar-drop-down-list "$:/tags/ViewToolbar" "$:/config/ViewToolbarButtons/Visibility/">>
</div>
</div>"""/>